Package cs.eng1.piazzapanic.food.interfaces

Interface Cookable

All Superinterfaces:
Holdable
All Known Implementing Classes:
BasicCookable, Potato, UncookedPizza
public interface Cookable extends Holdable
A Holdable that can be cooked in an oven. Ingredients that implement this must have 2-step processing logic.
Author:
Andrey Samoilov, Ross Holmes
